NETWORK ID     NAME      DRIVER    SCOPE
7403f6b74f30   bridge    bridge    local        ***** the default network
f9f9a99c2c85   host      host      local
0f1d053a3f91   none      null      local

1) Default bridge network 
2) host network 
3) none network



